# Northwestern Pie Chart Component - Phase 2 Core Foundation
**Agent 2.1 - Scratchpad for Parallel Coordination**

## Component API Contract

### NorthwesternPieChart Component Interface
```javascript
interface NorthwesternPieChartProps {
  antibiotic: EnhancedAntibiotic;        // Required: antibiotic data from EnhancedAntibioticData.js
  size: 'small' | 'medium' | 'large';    // Required: responsive size variant
  onSegmentHover?: (segment: string, coverage: number, clinicalContext: string) => void;
  onSegmentClick?: (segment: string, antibiotic: EnhancedAntibiotic) => void;
  showLabels?: boolean;                  // Optional: show segment labels (default: false)
  interactive?: boolean;                 // Optional: enable hover/click (default: true)
  className?: string;                    // Optional: additional CSS classes
}
```

### 8-Segment Northwestern Categories
1. **MRSA** (0°-45°) - Methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus aureus
2. **VRE_faecium** (45°-90°) - Vancomycin-resistant Enterococcus faecium
3. **anaerobes** (90°-135°) - Bacteroides, C. difficile, mixed anaerobes
4. **atypicals** (135°-180°) - Legionella, Mycoplasma, Chlamydophila
5. **pseudomonas** (180°-225°) - Pseudomonas aeruginosa
6. **gramNegative** (225°-270°) - Gram-negative organisms
7. **MSSA** (270°-315°) - Methicillin-sensitive Staphylococcus aureus
8. **enterococcus_faecalis** (315°-360°) - Enterococcus faecalis

### Coverage Scale Visual Mapping
- **0** = No coverage: White fill, gray border
- **1** = Poor/moderate coverage: Light fill color, solid border  
- **2** = Good coverage: Dark fill color, solid border
- **Cell wall active**: Dotted border pattern (beta-lactams, vancomycin, daptomycin)

### Route Color Integration
- **Oral**: Red-based color palette
- **IV**: Blue-based color palette  
- **Both**: Purple-based color palette

### Responsive Size Specifications
- **Small (mobile)**: 120px diameter, minimal labels
- **Medium (tablet)**: 200px diameter, abbreviated labels
- **Large (desktop)**: 280px diameter, full labels

### DOM Structure for Styling (Agent 2.3)
```html
<div class="northwestern-pie-chart northwestern-pie-chart--{size} {className}">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 280 280" class="northwestern-pie-chart__svg">
    <!-- 8 path elements for segments -->
    <path class="pie-segment pie-segment--mrsa pie-segment--coverage-{0|1|2}" />
    <path class="pie-segment pie-segment--vre-faecium pie-segment--coverage-{0|1|2}" />
    <!-- ... remaining segments -->
    
    <!-- Center label -->
    <g class="pie-center-label">
      <text class="pie-center-label__name">{antibiotic.name}</text>
      <text class="pie-center-label__route">{route}</text>
    </g>
    
    <!-- Optional segment labels -->
    <g class="pie-segment-labels" style="display: {showLabels ? 'block' : 'none'}">
      <!-- Label elements -->
    </g>
  </svg>
  
  <!-- Loading state -->
  <div class="northwestern-pie-chart__loading" style="display: none">
    Loading...
  </div>
  
  <!-- Error state -->
  <div class="northwestern-pie-chart__error" style="display: none">
    Error loading chart
  </div>
</div>
```

### Event Handler Signatures (Agent 2.2)
```javascript
// Hover events
onSegmentHover(segmentName: string, coverage: number, clinicalContext: string)

// Click events  
onSegmentClick(segmentName: string, antibiotic: EnhancedAntibiotic)

// Internal events for animations
onAnimationStart(segmentName: string)
onAnimationComplete(segmentName: string)
```

### Performance Characteristics (Agent 2.4)
- **Rendering Target**: <1000ms for full chart render
- **Re-render**: <200ms for data changes
- **Memory**: <50MB for 30 concurrent charts
- **Animation**: 60fps smooth transitions

### Accessibility Requirements
- ARIA labels for each segment
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader compatible descriptions
- High contrast mode support

## Medical Data Integration

### EnhancedAntibioticData.js Structure
```javascript
{
  id: number,
  name: string,
  northwesternSpectrum: {
    MRSA: 0|1|2,
    VRE_faecium: 0|1|2, 
    anaerobes: 0|1|2,
    atypicals: 0|1|2,
    pseudomonas: 0|1|2,
    gramNegative: 0|1|2,
    MSSA: 0|1|2,
    enterococcus_faecalis: 0|1|2
  },
  cellWallActive: boolean,
  routeColor: 'red'|'blue'|'purple',
  route: string[]
}
```

## Integration Points for Other Agents

### Agent 2.2 (Interactions) Dependencies
- Component event handlers must be stable references
- Hover states need immediate visual feedback capability
- Click events should provide complete antibiotic data

### Agent 2.3 (Visual Design) Dependencies  
- CSS class structure must be consistent
- Color variables must be customizable
- Responsive breakpoints must be standardized

### Agent 2.4 (Animations) Dependencies
- SVG elements must have unique IDs for targeting
- Animation states need distinct CSS classes
- Performance metrics for animation timing

### Agent 2.5 (Integration) Dependencies
- Component must work within existing ErrorBoundary
- PropTypes validation must be comprehensive
- No conflicts with existing component styles

